import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"redis"}}>{`Redis`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Function`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Command`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Install`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`brew install redis`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Run server`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`redis-server /usr/local/etc/redis.conf`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Uninstall`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`brew uninstall redis && rm ~/Library/LaunchAgents/homebrew.mxcl.redis.plist`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Info`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`brew info redis`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
